<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Confirmação de Conta</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #007bff;
        }

        .confirmation-box {
            background-color: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            max-width: 600px;
        }

        .question {
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .btn-confirm {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="confirmation-box">
        <h1><%= mensagem %></h1>
        <div class="question">
            <p>Você realmente deseja ativar sua conta?</p>
            <form action="/confirmar-ativacao" method="post">
                <input type="hidden" name="token" value="<%= token %>">
                <button type="submit" class="btn-confirm">Sim, confirmar ativação</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>